    <item>
      <title>洛伊研究所称中国在亚洲的影响力已低于美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/china-s-power-in-asia-plateauing-below-us-lowy-institute-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据洛伊研究所对亚洲地区影响力的年度分析，由于中国经济实力受到限制，其在亚洲的影响力正稳定在低于美国的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/china-s-power-in-asia-plateauing-below-us-lowy-institute-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场乐观 南非联合政府成立百日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日是南非新政府执政的第 100 天，虽然联盟政府被认为提振了市场人气，但可以说，总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 先前的改革才是推动当前乐观情绪的因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 11:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对者考虑谴责议案，法国政府面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的新政府立即引起各政治派别的愤怒反应，增加了政府迅速垮台的风险，这将进一步给法国紧张的公共财政前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
